Directory structure
===================
   test_2d_af_cartesian         -- executable
   afsim2d_cartesian_sdf.nml    -- input file (swirling deformational flow)
   afsim2d_cartesian_sdf.gnu    -- gnuplot script
   README                       -- info (this file)
   run/                         -- simulation directory

HOWTO
=====
0. Create simulation directory if missing, and move into it
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run

1. Run simulation within directory
     $ ../test_2d_af_cartesian ../afsim2d_cartesian_sdf

2. Run included gnuplot script
     $ gnuplot --persist ../afsim2d_cartesian_sdf.gnu

3. Open *.xmf database with Visit (*)


(*) Make sure that the Xdmf plugin is installed!

